text: I would just avoid it altogether
Underrated fact that the creator of Slenderman apparently lived in Japan when he came up with the concept of him

Dmitry Galkovsky said it, but if a mortician goes to live in China for a few years, if you ask him what life is like there, he'll start telling you about crematoriums and mausoleums. It will be a mortician's tale. It's always like this in life. Everyone has his own thing he sees.
